{
  "id": "RAW_729d43e6",
  "title": "Cursor 2.0 的一些有趣的新特性",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247499339&idx=1&sn=a0816c8fb3e2dcf66d84b49677562020",
  "date": "2025-10-30 04:12:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem;\">大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">Cursor 2.0版本来了，有一点一雪前耻的感觉，重新在短短一天内收获了大量用户的好评。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">该版本引入的新功能很多，我们这里简单看几个亮点。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">省流版</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">1. 自研的Composer模型强大，能力略逊于sonnet 4.5，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">编码速度是普通的4倍以上</span>。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">2. 可以<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">并发开启多任务</span>，不用担心它们互相干扰。(通过worktree实现)</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">3.&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">集成内置浏览器</span>，极大提升界面类编码工作的效率。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">4.&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">内置语音识别功能</span>。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">5. 做了一个新界面叫\"Agents模式\"，隐藏了代码编辑区，允许用户专注于聊天，没事就别看代码了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">整体感受是：Cursor团队可真懂Vibe Coding啊哈哈哈哈！</span></span></p>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">Composer 1 模型： 光速、强大、略微尴尬</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">过去几个月，Claude Code带头做了包月套餐、让用户不断从Cursor流失，这可能让Cursor团队进一步提升了自己训练模型的紧迫性。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">Cursor团队这次做得很棒。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">Cursor自己训练的代码模型改名叫了Composer 1。 写代码能力的确很能打，速度也很快。它以前的代号是cheetah。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">速度达到了200 token/s。要知道，在以前，其他代码模型，超过100 token/s的都已经是很快了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">我简单录屏，大家感受一下速度。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">下面两个录屏，皆为原速。第一个是在新的界面Agents模式下，第二个录屏是在传统界面侧边栏。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015681\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5949953660797034\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=19e2906f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2F607DKnuWzlGCOLznJIUa9QA8dvOiaW3KKNQ50eMs01XBKsEzktR749QwM3qyUGkJYSrOWWpTgrVeEPqiaI8Gzf3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015688\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.375\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ea54f9d9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2F607DKnuWzlGCOLznJIUa9QA8dvOiaW3KK1AWApUicialWoWptNqlsiaGA599KHqhcftoFOLX87CtlopKGIcicZeUwiaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">但是，除了速度，我不知道我为什么需要用它。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">按照Cursor官方的说法，Composer模型的能力，虽然有提升、但是仍然打不过世界最强模型。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015676\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5787037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b2364822&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGCOLznJIUa9QA8dvOiaW3KKM5Gdfz2n2UQBDEHq5GOYib9JlCIDFPOCJ9Z5zYDZIpyqdIMP5F6EibicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">这就非常别扭了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">在Cursor里，使用Composer 1模型，和使用Sonnet 4.5模型，消耗的积分是一样的，都是1倍积分（如下图所示）。&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">同样的价格，我为什么不选择更好的Sonnet 4.5模型呢？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015674\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6690307328605201\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"846\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1fa90e5a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGCOLznJIUa9QA8dvOiaW3KKshYRxR0XCN4joy9mThBKs9keIJ54MQAe3oL4VBAtI6NTOX4A5Rr4iaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015675\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.725\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"880\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9887d9f1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGCOLznJIUa9QA8dvOiaW3KKicsNib5iaK0lKFFQyvm7wua7ExPThMNYWcVS38SDjJ57Kublp2NsScEag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;3 1 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">并行模式：在平行时空开启多个任务，不互相干扰</span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">有技术背景的同学可能已经想到了，其实它只是一个 Git Worktree功能的套壳而已。</span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">技术实现虽然简单，但是真的好用啊！ 点击选择一下就来了，尤其是对于新手来说，可太方便。1</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015682\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5839243498817966\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"846\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9633907a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGCOLznJIUa9QA8dvOiaW3KKzDbxQiauFgaicrcvxAFDlSQNXa71ic4624UNpWOGK0FKEL9eTDic31VJyA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"3 1 []\">\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">内置浏览器：改善界面调整类编码工作的效率</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">这是本次Cusor更新我最喜欢的一个功能，它把以前需要stagewise等插件做的事情，官方下场做了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015679\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5919811320754716\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"848\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b972e1b8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGCOLznJIUa9QA8dvOiaW3KKbpcy8LQEphJmstMUKDC87p1PQ3z7d8kP2KCUXFpb9bialPBoAA8QutA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">打开内置浏览器以后，右上角可以开启元素选择功能、Devtools功能。元素选择功能可以指哪打哪儿，工作方式符合直觉。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015678\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5694444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a77ff6c5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGCOLznJIUa9QA8dvOiaW3KKibqO98X4JS2CbaMV40EdPHPetHqyCA2cfHS2CmBrbqGcn7oloGOl0aQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">虽然截图只体现了“指哪儿打哪儿”功能，它远比“指哪儿打哪儿”更加厉害。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">Cursor内置浏览器还做到了：</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">-&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">日志处理</span>。浏览器日志会写入文件，</span><span leaf=\"\">Agent 可通过 grep 有选择地读取。不再在每次操作后总结冗长输出，而是只读取所需的相关行。既保留完整上下文，又最大限度减少 token 使用。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">-&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">开发服务器感知</span>。 Cursor内置浏览器可以自动感知到当前启动服务的端口。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">-&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">设计转代码</span>。 Cursor有了内置浏览器，就等同于有了“眼睛”。我们可以通过 “</span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:italic;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:cursorSans, &quot;cursorSans Fallback&quot;, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">@browser 分析该设计稿，提取配色与字体系统，生成像素级还原的 HTML 和 CSS 代码</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">”&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这样的方式，把设计图变成代码</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">使用注意事项</span>：根据Cursor官方文档，使用内置浏览器功能时，请你选择sonnet 4.5、GPT-5 (而不是它自己的composer模型），能取得更好的效果。</span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">语音识别：速度快、精度高的语音识别，自动转换为英文</span></span></p>\n   <div>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">在Cursor 2.0的右侧多了一个语音按钮。</span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">非常有趣！</span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">首先，它的识别速度又快又准，这很好。Cursor团队真的很懂Vibe Coding! &nbsp;</span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">有趣的是： 当我们说中文，它会自动上屏英文</span>。😄 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">不知道为啥会如此设计？哈哈哈哈</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015686\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4772234273318872\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"922\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=da0146e6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGCOLznJIUa9QA8dvOiaW3KKtKvPgwOfI8C0w5eRia7wJYr84SMMktMvSs9p6Wxo56rvA7WCA8kicZFA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015687\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4708423326133909\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"926\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b01602f6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGCOLznJIUa9QA8dvOiaW3KKaLa4oxe5d7h0oBDI651ulZOqnfhYzNQMEc7yhofxvicCLmRQcJ57Jrw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">新增纯Agents模式：适合纯粹Vibe Coding人群</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">前几天我在线下课的时候，发现一些没有技术功底的朋友，它们会关掉Cursor/VS Code的代码编辑区域，让他屏幕上的主要显示区域是聊天。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">因为代码编辑、代码预览区域，对他们来说，没什么用。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">正在感慨世界变化大呢，没想到，Cursor自己把这功能也给做了</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">是的，Cursor 2.0引入了一个单独的模式 —— 与其说是“模式”，不如说是“界面” —— Agents模式，只让你关注聊天，不给你看代码了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">如下图所示。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015690\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5694444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=15e1a39c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlGCOLznJIUa9QA8dvOiaW3KKiaFZqgIh3X3A1YI2ribUIluqEtcyfu5gQaGMiazjZDI0L1IibW5bKSIicCw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">没想好还挺好用的，产品体验做得很好。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">如果你是没有代码基础的同学，可以试试。</span></p>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">总评：很好！我决定续费Cursor。</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">特别提醒：</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">考虑到Cursor的价格策略很抠是既成事实，我们仍然需要用Claude Code或者Codex，才能够满足更高的工作量。</span></p>\n   <div>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">期待你的反馈。</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章详细评测了 AI 辅助编程工具 Cursor 2.0 版本的多项创新功能，包括自研模型、并行模式、内置浏览器和 Agents 模式，并分享了作者的使用体验和续费决定。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章详细评测了 AI 辅助编程工具 Cursor 2.0 版本的多项创新功能，包括自研模型、并行模式、内置浏览器和 Agents 模式，并分享了作者的使用体验和续费决定。",
  "summary": "本文深度解析了 AI 辅助编程工具 Cursor 2.0 版本带来的多项关键更新。作者刘小排首先概括了新版本亮点：自研 Composer 模型的高速编码能力、通过 Worktree 实现的并发多任务处理、集成内置浏览器显著提升界面类编码效率、内置语音识别以及为非技术用户设计的纯 Agents 模式。文章详细介绍了 Composer 1 模型虽然速度快，但能力略逊于顶尖模型且积分消耗相同导致的性价比困境。随后，重点阐述了并行模式、内置浏览器（支持日志处理、开发服务器感知、设计转代码）和语音识别功能的实用性。最后，作者肯定了新增的 Agents 模式对纯聊天 Vibe Coding 人群的友好度，并总结决定续费 Cursor，但也提醒用户在工作量大时仍需结合其他工具使用。整体而言，文章对 Cursor 2.0 的新特性进行了全面而实用的评测。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Cursor 自研 Composer 1 模型实现高速编码，但能力与顶尖模型有差距。",
      "explanation": "Composer 1 模型编码速度高达 200 token/s，显著提升效率，但其代码生成能力仍不及 Sonnet 4.5，且积分消耗相同，导致性价比略显尴尬。"
    },
    {
      "point": "并行模式基于 Git Worktree 实现，极大简化多任务开发流程。",
      "explanation": "该模式允许用户在不互相干扰的情况下并发开启多个开发任务，虽然技术实现是 Git Worktree 的套壳，但其易用性对新手尤其友好。"
    },
    {
      "point": "内置浏览器集成开发功能，大幅提升界面类编码效率。",
      "explanation": "该功能集成了元素选择、Devtools、日志处理和开发服务器感知，并支持设计稿转代码，是前端开发者提升工作效率的利器。"
    },
    {
      "point": "新增 Agents 模式，为非技术背景用户提供纯聊天式编程体验。",
      "explanation": "该模式隐藏了代码编辑区，让用户专注于与 AI 聊天交互，极大提升了'Vibe Coding'体验，降低了技术门槛，特别适合初学者或寻求纯粹聊天式编程的用户。"
    }
  ],
